high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the closest large metal spoon off of the counter.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the large metal spoon on the grey plate in the sink.
Pick up the grey plate with the large metal spoon on it out of the sink.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the grey plate with the large spoon on it onto the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a grey plate with a large metal spoon on it on the counter.

high_descs: Look down, turn right and walk to the microwave to your right.
Grab the ladle next to the microwave on the counter.
Turn right, and walk to the sink to your left.
Place the ladle on the plate in the sink.
Pick up the plate with the ladle on it.
Turn right and make a quick left to face the counter.
Place the plate with the ladle on it on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a ladle on it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the right, and right quickly to face the counter.
Pick up the ladle from the front of the counter.
Carry the ladle and take a step to the right to face the sink.
Place the ladle on the plate, that is inside the sink.
Pick up the plate from inside the sink.
Hold the plate and take a step to the right.
Place the ladle and plate on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate and ladle to the counter.
